      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOMMIE'S BRIDE (1) was in the placings last time but three back produced an outstanding 17.29 win over 300m at this track. Expected to push the clock again here. MIDNIGHT DASH (8) made light work of a wide draw last time with a strong early sectional and clocking 17.47 in a 4.5 lengths win at this track over 300m. Expecting another bold showing. GOLDEN SUNSET (2) had some strong recent form but was below best last time when fourth (17.70) in a Grade 3/4 at this track. Generally a good beginner but was buried in the ruck off the inside last time. Solid record here at the distance winning seven races. Has the ability to give this a shake. WONDER KID (6) is a last-start placegetter who is in the mix again.",
